* ''Nemesis'', a [[Nemesis (Icon Comics)#Film|planned film adaptation]] of the Mark Millar graphic novel
* ''[[Star Trek: Nemesis]]'', a 2002 film, the 10th ''Star Trek'' movie
* [[Nemesis (Star Trek: Voyager)|"Nemesis" (''Star Trek: Voyager)'']], episode 4 of season 4 of the 1995 science fiction series
* [[Nemesis (Stargate SG-1)|"Nemesis" (''Stargate SG-1'')]], episode 22 of season 3 of the 1997 science fiction series
* Nemesis, the UN organisation ''[[The Champions]]'' worked for in the 1960s British television spy drama
* [[Nemesis (Xena and Hercules)]],  a recurring character in the television series ''Hercules: The Legendary Journeys''
* [[Nemesis (TV series)|''Nemesis'' (TV series)]], a British-American TV spy drama from BBC and Cinemax

